g.text: Integration Test Anatomy: Source Mapping to Token Stream

ol.li: Whitespace Invariant: Spaces at indices 03, 06, 09, 12, 14, 16, 23, 29 are consumed by _skip_whitespace() but never emitted.
Maximal Munch: The sequence > = at indices 07-08 is consumed as a single GREATER_EQ token because _match('=') returns True.
EOF Invariant: The \0 null terminator at index 31 ensures a terminal EOF token is emitted, allowing the parser to terminate gracefully.
